    <article>

      <p><strong>Hello!</strong>, we're halfway through this season, and we're taking another shot at sharing some comics with some of you that didn't get a chance to subscribe</p>
      <p>We've set up a nice instagram that could do with some attention, so this time we're giving away the last three comics to anyone who either</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Follows us over here on <a href="https://www.instagram.com/minicomic.club/">instagram/minicomic.club</a></li>
