      <p>This month we have <strong>Joshua Santospirito's</strong> <em>I Wanna Be A Travella</em>, <strong>Kathy Sarpi's</strong> untitled mini and <strong>Freda Chiu's</strong> <em>Necroman</em> - get in by <strong>25th June</strong> and you could have all three of these finding their way to your mailbox!</p>
      <p>We'll also send you a nice risograph poster that <a href="http://heliopress.bigcartel.com/">Ashley</a> made for us.</p>

